{"tid":2456750,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"BBC News 中文 中美關係：為何南海是兵家必爭之地？","createTime":"2021-03-22T07:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T07:06:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d8deb7db1b94ffca431d5bab01a28e153bbe3d60","tid":2456750,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T07:05:08.000Z","msg":"BBC News 中文<br />\n中美關係：為何南海是兵家必爭之地？<br />\n－ BBC News 中文<br />\nMar 19, 2021<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W1u1rEzK4Wo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DW1u1rEzK4Wo&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbZ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=43f3b3ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W1u1rEzK4Wo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBBC News 中文<br />\n835K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n南海是世界上爭端最多的區域之一。中國宣示擁有南海90%海域的主權，地區內的其他領土聲索方並不同意，美國也加入這場較量。<br />\n<br />\n最近，中國在南海展開為期一個月的密集軍演，是該海域罕見的長期演習，以此回應美軍在南海的「航行自由行動」。美國則與日本、澳大利亞、印度組成的「四方安全對話機制」接觸密切，以抗衡中國的影響力。<br />\n<br />\n超級大國在此針鋒相對，南海因此被認為是中美軍事衝突「第一張多米諾骨牌」。BBC中文駐北美記者馮兆音為你解讀，南海緣何是兵家必爭之地？<br />\n<br />\n視頻製作：喬&middot;佩恩（Joe Payne）<br />\n<br />\nBBC News 中文: <a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%E2%80%8B&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbZ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=aa9cb411\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%E2%80%8B&h=34013540\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen​</a><br />\n訂閱BBC News 中文 YouTube：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/1wkHh5T​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F1wkHh5T%E2%80%8B&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbZ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=b5d096a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/1wkHh5T​</a><br />\nBBC News 中文 Facebook - <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bbcchinese​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbbcchinese%E2%80%8B&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbZ1QB7Ma9ovE6n